Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,开幕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.53,0:00:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我儿子就是不肯叫我老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,还把老家给烧掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.29,0:00:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我儿子也一个人离家出走不回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.63,0:00:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,家家有本难念的经啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,老板 来块油炸豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我要鱼肉山芋片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:38.10,TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}来我家坐坐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.63,0:00:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你其实很怕孤独吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.64,0:00:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,人家哪有这样子~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:01.79,TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}变身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,看来要动真格的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.82,0:01:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说这把武器我用得还不太熟练…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法变身~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,纯真可爱☆布拉德雷~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:25.48,TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}胡爷爷之死!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这下死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,老夫命不久矣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,至少给兰芳留下点什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,爷爷！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,咽气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.63,0:01:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,爷爷！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:50.17,TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}巴卡尼亚之死!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,古利麟加入了我们这边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:01:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:01:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这下我死而无憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.81,0:02:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我心里再也没有什么遗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快去向作战总部投降 快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢您 上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 人生唯一一次桃花运错过了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉！
